As of the census<ref name=census2010/> of 2010, there were 685 people living in the CDP. There were 226 housing units. The [[Race and ethnicity in the United States Census|racial makeup]] of the CDP was 96.4% White, 1.0% American Indian and Alaska Native, 1.8% from some other race, and 0.9% from two or more races. Hispanic or Latino of any race were 3.6% of the population.

